# vhs demo.tape → demo.gif  (https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs)
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1150
Set Height 720
Set Padding 12
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "# Make your API agent-ready: discover → sign up → use. Zero humans."
Enter
Sleep 1.5s
Type "node examples/demo.mjs"
Enter
Sleep 9s
Type "node src/cli.js score examples/todo-api.yaml"
Enter
Sleep 5s
